snippet.title: Armed and Gelatinous Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Earth has finally declared World Peace and has made the rational decision to do away with all weapons by launching them into outer space. It seemed like a good idea at the time. That was until they were discovered by an alien race of space jelly!

Take on your friends in this highly competitive fast-paced bullet-hell game of blob warfare in the far reaches of space! Stock up on a variety of weapons, trading agility for firepower while dodging waves of bullets and deadly dash attacks from all angles! It's Armed and Gelatinous!

Join our Discord!
https://discord.gg/blobsonline

Find us on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/446510/Armed_and_Gelatinous/

Visit our Website!
http://www.armedandgelatinous.com
